    <div class="lesson-section" id="code">
        <div class="section-title-row"><div class="section-icon">💻</div><h2>דוגמת קוד</h2></div>
        <div class="code-box">
            <div class="code-label">🐍 Python — שיעור 10</div>
            <pre><span class="code-comment"># כתיבה לקובץ</span>
<span class="code-keyword">with</span> open(<span class="code-string">"students.txt"</span>, <span class="code-string">"w"</span>) <span class="code-keyword">as</span> f:
    f.write(<span class="code-string">"מיה, 18\n"</span>)
    f.write(<span class="code-string">"נועה, 17\n"</span>)
    f.write(<span class="code-string">"תמר, 19\n"</span>)

<span class="code-comment"># קריאה מהקובץ</span>
<span class="code-keyword">with</span> open(<span class="code-string">"students.txt"</span>, <span class="code-string">"r"</span>) <span class="code-keyword">as</span> f:
    content = f.read()
    <span class="code-keyword">print</span>(content)

<span class="code-comment"># קריאה שורה אחרי שורה</span>
<span class="code-keyword">with</span> open(<span class="code-string">"students.txt"</span>, <span class="code-string">"r"</span>) <span class="code-keyword">as</span> f:
    <span class="code-keyword">for</span> line <span class="code-keyword">in</span> f:
        <span class="code-keyword">print</span>(line.strip())  <span class="code-comment"># strip מסיר \n</span>

<span class="code-comment"># הוספה לקובץ קיים (לא מוחק)</span>
<span class="code-keyword">with</span> open(<span class="code-string">"students.txt"</span>, <span class="code-string">"a"</span>) <span class="code-keyword">as</span> f:
    f.write(<span class="code-string">"דנה, 18\n"</span>)</pre>
        </div>
        <div class="project-box">
            <h3>🛠️ פרויקט קטן — סיום Level 2!</h3>
            <p>תוכנית שמבקשת 3 שמות חברות וגיל, שומרת ל-friends.txt, וקוראת ומדפיסה:<br><br>
            <code style="background:#FFF0F5;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:8px;color:#D81B60;font-family:monospace;font-size:0.85rem;display:block;">friends = []<br>for _ in range(3):<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;name = input("שם: ")<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;age = int(input("גיל: "))<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;friends.append(f"{name}, {age}")<br>with open("friends.txt", "w") as f:<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;for fr in friends:<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;f.write(fr + "\n")<br>with open("friends.txt", "r") as f:<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;print(f.read())</code></p>
        </div>
